Format[edit]

  • Knockouts:
    • 10 teams, Double-Elimination bracket
      • The top seed from EMEA and the Americas receive a bye into round 2
    • All matches (excl. Lower Bracket Final and Grand Final) are Bo3
    • Lower Bracket Final and Grand Final are Bo5
